        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 24 at 8:31PM CDT until July 24 at 9:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 831 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Goodnight, or 9
miles southeast of Claude, moving northwest at 15 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Goodnight.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with this storm, and may lead to
flash flooding. Do not drive your vehicle through flooded roadways.</instruction>
